    Interface definition for callbacks to be invoked when a request to Biometrics.convertToFMD(Bitmap input_image, FMDFormat format, OnConvertToFMDListener listener) returns with results.
    Biometrics.OnDecompressWSQListener

    Biometrics.OnFingerprintGrabbedListener

    Interface definition for a callback to be invoked when a request to Biometrics.getPreferences(String key, PreferencesListener listener) or Biometrics.setPreferences(String key, String value, PreferencesListener listener) has finished.
